{"tid":317523,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"《社會的自白》","createTime":"2017-07-11T13:29:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-14T15:53:41.000Z","uid":35668,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f1a46854e3bbab515919d64c3a37b5bcdf678dae","tid":317523,"uid":35668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T13:29:56.000Z","msg":"1.<br />\n<br />\n我尋找作為人的樂趣<br />\n撕破她的衣服<br />\n扼殺她的貞潔<br />\n原來早已<br />\n捨棄了人的尊嚴<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">〈羈留所內的強姦犯〉</div>"},{"pid":"f81e2bbeee69e305ee9d0376daa6cb9eeea665bf","tid":317523,"uid":35668,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T15:07:01.000Z","msg":"2.<br />\n沙沙之聲<br />\n猶言在耳<br />\n洪水已襲來<br />\n不宜留此地<br />\n<br />\n猛獸之影<br />\n近在眼前<br />\n三面皆是牆<br />\n只能留此地<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">〈管道內的兩名工人〉</div>"},{"pid":"113f54091359061864b194af77ef2cd2ec9b1ee6","tid":317523,"uid":73490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T16:13:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2.<br />\n沙沙之聲<br />\n猶言在耳<br />\n洪水已襲來<br />\n不宜留此地<br />\n<br />\n猛獸之影<br />\n近在眼前<br />\n三面皆是牆<br />\n只能留此地<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">〈管道內的兩名工人〉</div></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d65b2be16f404036b428fbcad44f2eeba94f452","tid":317523,"uid":35668,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T00:43:25.000Z","msg":"3.<br />\n<br />\n成功的人談結果<br />\n失敗的人談過程<br />\n年青人談戀愛<br />\n在前方沒有光明的環境下<br />\n你還和我<br />\n談什麼未來呢<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">〈應屆DSE考生〉</div>"},{"pid":"9c76f5f084b1376a70e5a4a0c732269f0425cbb5","tid":317523,"uid":35668,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T15:20:47.000Z","msg":"4.<br />\n<br />\n你不會相信<br />\n現在的我有多幸福<br />\n醫生、枕邊人、甚至遠在另一緯度的<br />\n都站在我的床邊支持我<br />\n遺憾的是<br />\n明天不在我的這邊<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">〈劉先生〉</div>"},{"pid":"22ea197a908add4f5dc40a7497ae730c56defaf0","tid":317523,"uid":40429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T15:30:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>4.<br />\n<br />\n你不會相信<br />\n現在的我有多幸福<br />\n醫生、枕邊人、甚至遠在另一緯度的<br />\n都站在我的床邊支持我<br />\n遺憾的是<br />\n明天不在我的這邊<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">〈劉先生〉</div></blockquote><br />\n呢個似樣返少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba068b4dbea2ec62723f475316712d689f9d0977","tid":317523,"uid":35668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T15:48:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>4.<br />\n<br />\n你不會相信<br />\n現在的我有多幸福<br />\n醫生、枕邊人、甚至遠在另一緯度的<br />\n都站在我的床邊支持我<br />\n遺憾的是<br />\n明天不在我的這邊<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">〈劉先生〉</div></blockquote><br />\n呢個似樣返少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49e856b85d1ee8ebc3c67c036b2dd4b0e00e11ea","tid":317523,"uid":4610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T19:24:18.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"491b24969d9c908ce90e7f1d1375917df6d216bb","tid":317523,"uid":35668,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T14:43:43.000Z","msg":"5.<br />\n<br />\n客人<br />\n你走失的貓被困在紙箱內<br />\n活著<br />\n同時也被毒死了<br />\n機率是百分之五十<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">動物傳心師A</div>"},{"pid":"7da78b8b603448e279abda8175de42c298e2ed8b","tid":31